<li>Sending you love and strength as you grieve the loss of your father.</li>
<li>With deepest sympathy, wishing you peace and comfort in the days ahead.</li>
<li>Your father was a special man, and his memory will always be cherished.</li>
<li>I am so saddened by the news of your father's passing. He was a true inspiration.</li>
